Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.74,0:00:29.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像有点色情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.01,0:00:31.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,买看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.21,0:00:34.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐比较漂亮啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.88,0:00:37.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说甚么阿   身材好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.02,0:00:40.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳不用打扮很棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.02,0:00:43.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然要打扮阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.89,0:00:46.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都不用阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.36,0:00:48.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪有阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.63,0:00:51.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近买甚么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.77,0:00:53.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这好可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.77,0:00:56.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢可爱内衣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.18,0:01:05.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪一个比较
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.98,0:01:08.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪一个阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.33,0:01:19.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻由美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.59,0:01:24.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我差不多该睡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.60,0:01:28.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳还不睡阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.67,0:01:31.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还想和惠里加看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.81,0:01:35.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.88,0:01:39.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.21,0:01:46.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惠里加的老公也快回家了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.42,0:01:48.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.89,0:01:51.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.50,0:02:00.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感情真棒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.57,0:02:06.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.57,0:02:09.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.45,0:02:12.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.05,0:02:20.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.59,0:02:26.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.26,0:02:30.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他像气了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.87,0:02:34.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点点吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.00,0:02:37.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怕寂寞吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.74,0:02:41.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生气了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.74,0:02:46.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近没做吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.35,0:02:52.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃多了吧   没事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.09,0:02:56.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.42,0:02:57.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像很适合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.29,0:03:00.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件有吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.83,0:03:02.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有吧   想要吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.43,0:03:05.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.50,0:03:14.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隔天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.72,0:03:24.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻由美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.25,0:03:26.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.52,0:03:28.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.86,0:03:39.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天那么晚睡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.07,0:03:42.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真早起阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.80,0:03:45.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.41,0:03:49.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻由美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.68,0:03:52.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前因为生理期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.88,0:03:55.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天第几天了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.42,0:03:59.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一大早就这样问
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.42,0:04:06.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得有这可能性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.90,0:04:11.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我每天都会算喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.83,0:04:15.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.24,0:04:21.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天想做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.84,0:04:27.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前说过了阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.25,0:04:31.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还不想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.32,0:04:35.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不这样说阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.52,0:04:37.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.06,0:04:44.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都结婚三年了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.33,0:04:47.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.01,0:05:01.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.55,0:05:04.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.76,0:05:13.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都这时间了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.76,0:05:14.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我该走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.16,0:05:21.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会好好补充体力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.50,0:05:22.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多吃点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.37,0:05:24.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等妳喔·
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.04,0:05:29.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.14,0:06:02.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.48,0:06:06.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天也很晚回家喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.62,0:06:09.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.35,0:06:11.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去姊姊家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.95,0:06:13.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.69,0:06:15.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样会造成麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.62,0:06:18.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要考虑喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.16,0:06:20.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.89,0:06:22.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说甚么阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.50,0:06:24.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.50,0:06:29.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐和我一起还比较幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.77,0:06:32.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是妳的想法吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.17,0:06:35.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彻也怎么想呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.85,0:06:40.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一早就这么囉嗦   我去姐姐家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.81,0:07:06.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姊姊早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.41,0:07:07.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.47,0:07:08.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.68,0:07:11.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那家伙   真烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.15,0:07:14.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是信二吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.88,0:07:18.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天也很晚回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.49,0:07:22.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还说要我考虑到妳们心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.16,0:07:24.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.43,0:07:24.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.83,0:07:25.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.09,0:07:25.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.36,0:07:25.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.63,0:07:25.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.76,0:07:26.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.69,0:07:29.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这没办法啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.36,0:07:34.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们太常见面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.44,0:07:39.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且住在隔壁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.04,0:07:46.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结婚之前   就在家每天见面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.85,0:07:48.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡在同张床
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.78,0:07:51.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在没有阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.85,0:07:53.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.19,0:07:56.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和之前相比的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.33,0:08:03.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了   我想问问
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.80,0:08:10.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得我生小孩怎样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.41,0:08:12.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.41,0:08:17.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姊姊想要吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.28,0:08:21.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.42,0:08:25.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彻也说想要孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.02,0:08:30.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是觉得太快了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.69,0:08:33.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.43,0:08:40.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彻也有点变了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.04,0:08:45.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还算我的生理期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.17,0:08:51.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还算内裤的数量
