Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.46,0:09:06.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.66,0:09:12.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会保护姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.80,0:09:21.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照我的话做吧
