Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.87,0:10:25.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.34,0:10:27.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.74,0:10:32.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有乖吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.22,0:10:41.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了今天我吃鳗鱼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.63,0:10:48.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有效果吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.50,0:10:53.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都变成这样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.30,0:10:59.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这边好害羞喔
