Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.58,0:11:12.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了今天晚上    我好好准备了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.74,0:11:30.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.88,0:11:37.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚餐呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.55,0:11:41.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下再吃吧
