Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.57,0:12:04.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好期待喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.25,0:12:14.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.65,0:12:17.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.39,0:12:23.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要幸福喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.67,0:12:38.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天有点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.54,0:12:41.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.14,0:12:46.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很想要做爱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.75,0:12:48.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要小孩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.31,0:13:16.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好兴奋喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.85,0:13:21.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,累积好多喔  是喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.85,0:13:23.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.59,0:13:29.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳兴奋的话   会生男生喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.59,0:13:35.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我想生男的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.93,0:13:39.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.00,0:13:46.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女生也可以    不过男生比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.28,0:13:50.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多爽一点吧
