Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.56,0:14:10.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天好厉害喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.70,0:14:14.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.24,0:14:17.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会让妳爽的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.85,0:14:28.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这身体好香喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.59,0:14:41.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太兴奋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.80,0:14:45.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.60,0:14:49.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要这样吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.74,0:14:55.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没见过这内衣喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.21,0:14:57.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.28,0:15:03.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样弄吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.02,0:15:07.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.37,0:15:21.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.97,0:15:27.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害羞吗
