Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.51,0:16:37.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样弄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.51,0:16:40.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边怎样了阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.26,0:16:54.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好开心喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.96,0:17:23.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.16,0:17:26.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我摸摸
